"    Lymphoma of bone",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 279px; height: 361px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Lateral plain film of the knee demonstrates a \"moth-eaten\" pattern in the proximal tibia at the metadiaphyseal junction, along with bone destruction (large arrow). An associated periosteal reaction is present (small arrow).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
